Package com.camerontec.catalys.util.marketdata

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDepthEntry
    Standard interface supported by any object representing an entry in a market depth.
    IDepthUpdate
    Classes maintaining an internal depth can allow the depth to be updated externally using these methods.
    IDetailEntry
    Standard interface supported by any object representing an entry in a market detail (unaggregated depth).
    IDetailUpdate
    Classes maintaining an internal detail can allow the detail to be updated externally using these methods.
    IFieldInfo
    Information about a Cameron market data field.
    IFieldInfos
    Provides additional information about a market data field given that field's ID.
    IFixFieldInfo  
    IFixFieldInfos
    Extension of standard IFieldInfos to support FIX related mapping information from market data fields.
    IFixMarketDataInstrument
    Interface for instruments that are stored in the Market Data Server when it is in Daisy Chain mode (i.e.
    IGroupFieldInfo  
    IGroupFieldInfos  
    IInstrument
    Represents an entity (eg a stock) that is traded on a market.
    IInstrumentDepthListener
    Objects that want to listen for depth or detail updates should implement this interface.
    IInstrumentLeg  
    IInstrumentMarketDataListener
    Base interface that all listeners to market data of any type must implement.
    IInstrumentSecurityDefinitionListener
    Objects that want to listen for security definition updates should implement this interface.
    IInstrumentTopOfBookListener
    Objects that want to listen for top of book updates should implement this interface.
    IMarketDataItem
    Basic unit of market data - adding a market data field id to a market data value.
    IMarketDataService
    A IService that reads market data from some source (eg a stock exchange feed or a third party such as Reuters) and stores that market data in a standard object.
    IMarketDataStore
    Stores market data (eg prices, trading status, etc) for a market.
    IMarketDataValue
    Basic market data value - consisting of a value and when that value was set.
    IPriceStepEntry
    A single price step entry in PriceStepInfo.
    IPriceStepInfo
    Information about price steps.
    ISecurityDefinition
    Represents security definition associated with an instrument on the market.
    ISecurityDefinitionUpdate
    Classes maintaining security definition data can allow it to be updated externally using these methods.
    ISubscriptionListener
    Market data services support this interface so that other objects can instruct them what subscriptions are required on their instruments.
    ITopOfBookUpdate
    Classes maintaining top of book data can allow it to be updated externally using these methods.
    ITradingSessionStatusListener
    Objects that want to listen for trading session updates should implement this interface.
    IUpdateEntry
    Interface supported by objects used to notify listeners of changes to top of book market data.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DecimalPlacesConversion
    Some utility methods for converting ints, longs to String's with decimal places.
    DetailEntry
    Standard implementation of IDetailEntry useful for passing into methods like IDetailUpdate.changeDetail or IDepthUpdate.changeDepth (as used in StandardInstrument).
    FieldInfo
    Standard implementation of IFieldInfo.
    FieldInfos
    Standard implementation of IFieldInfos which provides the field names for all standard market data fields.
    FixFieldInfo
    Standard implementation of IFixFieldInfo.
    FixFieldInfos
    Default market data IFieldInfos implementation.
    FixMarketDataInstrument
    Instrument class specific to the Market Data Server Daisy Chain, in which the source of Market Data is also FIX.
    GroupFieldInfo
    Standard implementation of IGroupFieldInfo.
    InstGroupFieldInfos
    Defines Instrument and Instrument Leg Fields in SecurityDefinition message
    InstrumentFieldInfos
    Defines FIX Tag value for instrument group fields in SecurityDefiniton message.
    InstrumentLegFieldInfos
    Defines FIX Tag value for instrument leg group fields in SecurityDefiniton message.
    InternalDepthEntry
    IDepthEntry implementation used internally by StandardInstrument.
    InternalDetailEntry
    IDetailEntry implementation used internally by StandardInstrument.
    PriceStepEntry
    An implementation of IPriceStepEntry.
    PriceStepInfo
    An implementation of IPriceStepInfo.
    StandardInstrument
    Standard implementation of IInstrument.
    StandardInstrumentLeg  
    StandardMarketDataItem
    Useful implementation of IMarketDataItem which also has methods for setting the values.
    StandardMarketDataStore
    Standard implementation of IMarketDataStore.
    StandardMarketDataValue
    Standard implementation of IMarketDataValue which allows values to be modified.
    StandardSecurityDefinition
    Standard implementation of ISecurityDefinition
    StandardUpdateEntry
    Useful implementation of IUpdateEntry which also has methods for setting the values of the update entry including the old value.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    SubscriptionException
    Used for synchronously reporting market data source subscription errors.
